{
  "page": "Hunnimore",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> Hunnimore's canon status is unclear: the character is cited only in <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Princess_and_the_Queen\" title=\"The Princess and the Queen\">The Princess and the Queen</a></i>, wheareas in <i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> he is never mentioned, being replaced by <a href=\"/index.php/Gerardys\" title=\"Gerardys\">Gerardys</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/50px-Maester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/75px-Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/100px-Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Maester</span><br />Hunnimore</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/50px-Maester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/75px-Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/100px-Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Princess_and_the_Queen\" title=\"The Princess and the Queen\">The Princess and the Queen</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Hunnimore</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">maester</a> who served at <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hunnimore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Fall_of_Dragonstone\" title=\"Fall of Dragonstone\">fall of Dragonstone</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Marston_Waters\" title=\"Marston Waters\">Marston Waters</a> seized the <a href=\"/index.php/Rookery\" title=\"Rookery\">rookery</a> to prevent Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Gerardys\" title=\"Gerardys\">Gerardys</a> or Hunnimore from sending <a href=\"/index.php/Raven\" title=\"Raven\">ravens</a>. After Marston prevented Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Alfred_Broome\" title=\"Alfred Broome\">Alfred Broome</a> from killing <a href=\"/index.php/Baela_Targaryen\" title=\"Baela Targaryen\">Baela Targaryen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Tom_Tangletongue\" title=\"Tom Tangletongue\">Tom Tangletongue</a> brought the girl to the maester for treatment.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hunnimore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.